hopobject.body: Could you transfer $1000 from my current account to my deposit account? sudden withdrawal paxil SIR – Vince Cable, the Business Secretary, tells us HS2’s costs are to be revisited to take into account Treasury requirements (“How HS2 will tear up rural Britain”, report, 21 July). While such a review is welcome, the Treasury’s Green Book specifically states that a full appraisal should be carried out at the initiation of this and other major infrastructure schemes.
